  "stacked_probability_descriptions": {
    "p_star_plus": "Stacked display probability: legacy blind no-draft p_star multiplied by (1 - independent p_out_binary), with a conservative experience adjustment that leaves early entrants unchanged, discounts older college profiles, and applies a smooth translation adjustment for size, efficiency, defensive-event, high-usage/low-creation risk, additive no-draft creator/low-out rescue signals, and a year-safe size-bucket prior adjustment.",
    "p_superstar": "Nested conditional probability: p_star_plus * P(superstar | star_plus), where the conditional is a LOYO logistic model trained on actual STAR+ players only (12-of-36 positives). Monotone p_superstar <= p_star_plus holds by construction; the old capped stack is kept as p_superstar_capped_stack_legacy for comparison."
  },
